of Environmental Protection,
Mr. Huo Xiaoyue.

00:26:05.350 --> 00:26:06.400
Meng Yaohui of Xinhai Group.

00:26:06.400 --> 00:26:06.900
Hello.

00:26:07.000 --> 00:26:07.920
Welcome, everyone,

00:26:07.920 --> 00:26:09.580
to Xinhai for the inspection.

00:26:10.030 --> 00:26:11.890
We look forward to your feedback.

00:26:12.380 --> 00:26:12.850
Okay.

00:26:13.790 --> 00:26:14.520
Let's begin.

00:26:15.380 --> 00:26:16.240
This way, please.

00:26:16.240 --> 00:26:16.840
After you.

00:26:21.640 --> 00:26:23.170
What's the situation here?

00:26:23.810 --> 00:26:24.980
After the mining ban was issued,

00:26:24.980 --> 00:26:26.700
we ensured strict compliance.

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:27.290
This is a batch of

00:26:27.290 --> 00:26:28.700
vehicles that have been
taken out of service.

00:26:28.700 --> 00:26:30.500
We haven't disposed of them yet.

00:26:31.350 --> 00:26:33.030
Is the officer in the back okay?

00:26:33.030 --> 00:26:33.760
Take it slow.

00:26:34.610 --> 00:26:35.090
Song,

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:35.440
come on,

00:26:35.440 --> 00:26:35.920
the oxygen tank!

00:26:35.920 --> 00:26:36.750
On it!

00:26:38.530 --> 00:26:39.160
I'm sorry.

00:26:39.610 --> 00:26:40.540
Xinhai Coal Mine

00:26:40.550 --> 00:26:41.920
is located at a high altitude.

00:26:41.920 --> 00:26:43.180
Since you just came up,

00:26:43.180 --> 00:26:44.610
you might feel a bit unwell.

00:26:44.610 --> 00:26:46.140
No rush. Let's walk slowly.

00:26:46.790 --> 00:26:47.070
Right.

00:26:47.070 --> 00:26:47.350
It's okay.

00:26:47.350 --> 00:26:48.070
Take it slow.

00:26:48.070 --> 00:26:49.130
Let's look around.

00:26:51.680 --> 00:26:52.260
Over here,

00:26:52.260 --> 00:26:53.660
the main area of Mine No. 2

00:26:53.680 --> 00:26:54.740
has been shut down.

00:26:56.420 --> 00:26:57.010
You can see

00:26:57.010 --> 00:26:58.540
that white area over there.

00:26:58.750 --> 00:27:00.350
That area stopped operations long ago.

00:27:00.350 --> 00:27:02.610
Currently, only this small

00:27:02.640 --> 00:27:03.410
corner area

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:04.940
is undergoing work of
clearing out stockpiles

00:27:04.940 --> 00:27:06.670
and disposing of outcrop coal.

00:27:07.380 --> 00:27:08.720
Since we have this inspection today,

00:27:08.720 --> 00:27:09.630
for safety reasons,

00:27:09.630 --> 00:27:11.070
we stopped work early.

00:27:12.440 --> 00:27:13.320
What do you mean by

00:27:13.320 --> 00:27:14.770
"disposing of outcrop coal"?

00:27:14.770 --> 00:27:16.460
Based on expert studies

00:27:16.550 --> 00:27:18.050
and to avoid wasting resources,

00:27:18.050 --> 00:27:19.240
following the principle of

00:27:19.240 --> 00:27:20.040
environmental conservation,

00:27:20.040 --> 00:27:21.500
we mined less than

00:27:21.530 --> 00:27:23.180
50,000 tons of outcrop coal.

00:27:23.640 --> 00:27:25.160
It is worth noting that

00:27:25.300 --> 00:27:26.580
all revenue from

00:27:26.610 --> 00:27:27.610
this outcrop coal

00:27:27.640 --> 00:27:29.400
is going to slope regreening.

00:27:30.440 --> 00:27:31.770
It helps cover

00:27:31.790 --> 00:27:33.920
the funding gap for slope management.

00:27:34.950 --> 00:27:35.850
Your approach

00:27:35.880 --> 00:27:37.240
is quite flexible.

00:27:38.290 --> 00:27:38.770
Indeed,

00:27:38.790 --> 00:27:40.720
we should allow some flexibility.

00:27:41.350 --> 00:27:43.150
The regreening work at this mine

00:27:43.350 --> 00:27:44.550
is on the right track.

00:27:44.700 --> 00:27:45.740
It is proceeding in a solid

00:27:45.740 --> 00:27:46.870
and orderly manner.

00:27:47.380 --> 00:27:48.510
The most obvious sign

00:27:48.510 --> 00:27:49.610
is that

00:27:49.720 --> 00:27:51.680
the air quality index

00:27:51.770 --> 00:27:52.790
has significantly improved.

00:27:52.790 --> 00:27:53.720
The air quality

00:27:54.160 --> 00:27:55.220
is much better now.

00:27:55.660 --> 00:27:56.660
Environmental work

00:27:56.660 --> 00:27:57.860
benefits the present

00:27:57.940 --> 00:27:58.880
and the future.

00:27:59.350 --> 00:28:00.550
For the mining area's

00:28:00.640 --> 00:28:02.010
ecological restoration project,

00:28:02.010 --> 00:28:03.070
we have also made

00:28:03.100 --> 00:28:04.230
long-term plans.

00:28:05.590 --> 00:28:06.500
The measures and plans

00:28:06.500 --> 00:28:08.420
adopted by your city

00:28:08.510 --> 00:28:09.570
are quite pragmatic

00:28:09.570 --> 00:28:10.530
and effective.

00:28:11.200 --> 00:28:12.810
This aligns with the requirements
from above

00:28:12.810 --> 00:28:14.680
and the city's actual situation.

00:28:16.660 --> 00:28:17.290
This mine is indeed

00:28:17.290 --> 00:28:18.700
at a high altitude.

00:28:19.140 --> 00:28:20.420
I see that some of you

00:28:20.590 --> 00:28:21.770
are not quite used to it.

00:28:21.770 --> 00:28:22.630
How about this?

00:28:22.770 --> 00:28:24.070
Let's go to their canteen

00:28:24.070 --> 00:28:25.010
for a work lunch.

00:28:25.530 --> 00:28:27.160
Then we'll go to Mine No. 1

00:28:27.180 --> 00:28:28.730
to check the regreening there.

00:28:28.730 --> 00:28:29.530
Just a moment.

00:28:29.760 --> 00:28:31.070
Our inspection team

00:28:31.250 --> 00:28:32.030
received a signed

00:28:32.030 --> 00:28:33.770
letter of complaint from the public,

00:28:33.770 --> 00:28:35.050
claiming they have found

00:28:35.050 --> 00:28:36.050
that Xinhai Coal Mine

00:28:36.050 --> 00:28:37.710
is engaged in illegal mining.

00:28:46.290 --> 00:28:46.860
Sir,

00:28:47.610 --> 00:28:48.560
during the recent

00:28:48.560 --> 00:28:49.810
rectification of small and medium-sized

00:28:49.810 --> 00:28:51.070
coal mines in the city,

00:28:51.220 --> 00:28:52.850
someone came to Xinhai

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:54.250
to disrupt production order

00:28:54.250 --> 00:28:55.050
and cause trouble.

00:28:55.050 --> 00:28:56.450
They were investigated.

00:28:56.920 --> 00:28:58.320
As for illegal mining...

00:28:59.510 --> 00:29:01.440
That is purely their imagination.

00:29:01.620 --> 00:29:02.510
As far as I know,

00:29:03.250 --> 00:29:04.160
in the city,

00:29:04.690 --> 00:29:05.760
there are indeed enthusiastic

00:29:05.760 --> 00:29:06.960
environmentalists.

00:29:07.510 --> 00:29:08.580
They feel

00:29:08.750 --> 00:29:10.030
the development of the coal industry

00:29:10.030 --> 00:29:11.160
leads to pollution,

00:29:11.740 --> 00:29:12.510
so

00:29:12.550 --> 00:29:14.290
in their call for
environmental protection,

00:29:14.290 --> 00:29:15.550
their course of action

00:29:16.640 --> 00:29:18.240
can be a bit radical at times.

00:29:23.960 --> 00:29:25.290
These are the materials

00:29:25.420 --> 00:29:27.880
and photos submitted by the whistleblower.

00:29:43.200 --> 00:29:43.950
Manager Meng,

00:29:43.950 --> 00:29:44.810
take a look.

00:29:45.120 --> 00:29:46.360
Is this Xinhai?

00:29:58.350 --> 00:29:59.310
These...

00:30:00.420 --> 00:30:01.550
do look a bit like us.

00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:04.080
You said earlier that

00:30:04.090 --> 00:30:04.900
Xinhai Coal Mine

00:30:04.900 --> 00:30:06.830
mined 50,000 tons of outcrop coal.

00:30:07.250 --> 00:30:07.750
Yes.

00:30:08.510 --> 00:30:09.180
Looking at

00:30:09.200 --> 00:30:10.610
the data on the registry,

00:30:11.120 --> 00:30:12.500
and based on a coal truck's

00:30:12.500 --> 00:30:14.460
carrying capacity of 50

00:30:14.760 --> 00:30:15.500
to 100 tons,

00:30:15.640 --> 00:30:17.370
a rough estimate would suggest

00:30:17.380 --> 00:30:18.260
it is likely far more than

00:30:18.260 --> 00:30:19.160
50,000 tons.

00:30:20.650 --> 00:30:23.130
And the nighttime traffic volume

00:30:23.210 --> 00:30:25.210
is two to three times that of the day.

00:30:25.700 --> 00:30:26.520
So

00:30:26.580 --> 00:30:28.230
how do you explain that?

00:30:31.740 --> 00:30:32.670
Is the data here

00:30:32.700 --> 00:30:33.510
accurate?

00:30:34.950 --> 00:30:36.020
Judging by the data

00:30:36.050 --> 00:30:37.570
on the registry,

00:30:38.440 --> 00:30:40.170
the coal transport volume does

00:30:40.510 --> 00:30:41.640
come into question.

00:30:41.890 --> 00:30:43.390
But the authenticity

00:30:43.420 --> 00:30:44.350
of this registry

00:30:45.810 --> 00:30:47.470
needs further verification.

00:30:49.860 --> 00:30:50.720
Vice Mayor Lin.

00:30:51.200 --> 00:30:51.930
Director Ma.

00:30:53.680 --> 00:30:54.420
Hurry up and

00:30:54.490 --> 00:30:55.820
set up a dedicated team.

00:30:56.290 --> 00:30:57.750
Investigate thoroughly.

00:30:57.750 --> 00:30:58.220
Yes.

00:30:58.820 --> 00:30:59.550
Confirm the mining

00:30:59.550 --> 00:31:00.790
and sales data,

00:31:01.270 --> 00:31:03.430
and report to the inspection team
as soon as possible.

00:31:03.430 --> 00:31:03.900
Okay.

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:12.660
Coming.

00:31:14.210 --> 00:31:15.080
Shao Yunfei!

00:31:19.310 --> 00:31:20.110
What's wrong?

00:31:20.610 --> 00:31:21.450
Was it you who gave the photos

00:31:21.450 --> 00:31:22.050
taken by Han

00:31:22.050 --> 00:31:23.380
to the inspection team?

00:31:25.570 --> 00:31:26.590
Yes, right.

00:31:27.870 --> 00:31:28.330
Han

00:31:28.350 --> 00:31:29.510
had a bad feeling when he

00:31:29.510 --> 00:31:30.810
received the call from the mine.

00:31:30.810 --> 00:31:32.510
He told me to act at my discretion

00:31:32.510 --> 00:31:33.310
and submit the materials

00:31:33.310 --> 00:31:34.160
in his name.

00:31:34.180 --> 00:31:35.690
So you just did?

00:31:36.150 --> 00:31:37.580
Well, I should have

00:31:37.610 --> 00:31:38.720
discussed it with you beforehand.

00:31:38.720 --> 00:31:39.260
But...

00:31:39.640 --> 00:31:40.610
this inspection

00:31:40.630 --> 00:31:41.610
was too sudden,

00:31:41.790 --> 00:31:42.770
so I didn't have time to tell you.

00:31:42.770 --> 00:31:43.640
Shao Yunfei,

00:31:44.590 --> 00:31:45.110
you've been

00:31:45.110 --> 00:31:45.850
an investigative journalist

00:31:45.850 --> 00:31:46.830
for so many years.

00:31:46.830 --> 00:31:47.820
How come you just

00:31:47.850 --> 00:31:49.160
don't get it?

00:31:49.850 --> 00:31:50.770
Han did capture

00:31:50.790 --> 00:31:51.450
something.

00:31:51.770 --> 00:31:52.810
But it definitely doesn't form

00:31:52.810 --> 00:31:54.100
a complete chain of evidence.

00:31:54.100 --> 00:31:55.040
Doing this now

00:31:55.070 --> 00:31:55.980
will only alert them

00:31:55.980 --> 00:31:57.780
and make them even more guarded.

00:31:57.790 --> 00:31:59.190
It will make gathering evidence

00:31:59.190 --> 00:32:00.350
even harder later on.

00:32:00.350 --> 00:32:01.480
Do you understand?

00:32:03.140 --> 00:32:03.960
"A complete chain of evidence"?

00:32:03.960 --> 00:32:04.660
Right.

00:32:06.350 --> 00:32:07.160
We've been investigating Xinhai

00:32:07.160 --> 00:32:07.860
for so long.

00:32:08.180 --> 00:32:09.270
And the result?

00:32:10.620 --> 00:32:11.880
Han has been detained.

00:32:12.070 --> 00:32:13.020
You've been kicked out of the task force

00:32:13.020 --> 00:32:14.420
and forced to take leave.

00:32:14.500 --> 00:32:15.310
And me?

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:16.130
I can only write

00:32:16.130 --> 00:32:17.080
what they want me

00:32:17.100 --> 00:32:17.750
to write.

00:32:17.920 --> 00:32:18.850
Other than that,

00:32:19.250 --> 00:32:20.400
anything involving Xinhai

00:32:20.400 --> 00:32:21.420
gets blocked.

00:32:22.210 --> 00:32:23.480
That they dare to do this—

00:32:23.480 --> 00:32:25.690
who knows how much protection they've got

00:32:25.690 --> 00:32:26.780
behind them?

00:32:27.420 --> 00:32:28.460
We finally have

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:30.220
the provincial environmental
inspection team here.

00:32:30.220 --> 00:32:31.620
Are we going to let them
get away with it again?

00:32:31.620 --> 00:32:32.150
What do you think

00:32:32.150 --> 00:32:32.960
those photos from Han

00:32:32.960 --> 00:32:33.740
can prove?

00:32:33.900 --> 00:32:35.200
I'm asking you—what can they prove?

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:36.400
Keep your voice down.

00:32:36.410 --> 00:32:38.000
Xinhai can just make up an excuse

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:39.240
and get away with it.

00:32:54.560 --> 00:32:55.490
Maybe.

00:32:56.900 --> 00:32:57.880
Maybe in the eyes

00:32:57.910 --> 00:32:58.710
of those people at Xinhai,

00:32:58.710 --> 00:32:59.350
we're just a few

00:32:59.350 --> 00:33:00.880
flies they can't get rid of.

00:33:01.440 --> 00:33:02.770
Maybe this complaint

00:33:04.160 --> 00:33:05.570
will end up being a waste of time,

00:33:05.570 --> 00:33:07.030
just a splash in the water.

00:33:07.640 --> 00:33:08.480
But does that mean

00:33:08.480 --> 00:33:09.070
we should just

00:33:09.070 --> 00:33:09.940
do nothing?

00:33:10.870 --> 00:33:11.720
I'm not telling you

00:33:11.720 --> 00:33:12.670
to do nothing.

00:33:13.240 --> 00:33:14.090
I just want you

00:33:14.220 --> 00:33:15.250
to be less reckless

00:33:15.250 --> 00:33:15.980
and think about Zhuling

00:33:15.980 --> 00:33:17.180
before you act.

00:33:17.210 --> 00:33:18.020
Am I reckless?

00:33:20.900 --> 00:33:21.630
When I first

00:33:21.660 --> 00:33:23.120
left the Mountain Patrol,

00:33:23.480 --> 00:33:24.500
Captain had me hand in

00:33:24.500 --> 00:33:25.370
his reserve work notes

00:33:25.370 --> 00:33:26.420
to the provincial authorities.

00:33:26.420 --> 00:33:27.590
Because he knew

00:33:27.610 --> 00:33:29.240
we'd only get one chance.

00:33:30.160 --> 00:33:31.360
Giving it one try

00:33:32.180 --> 00:33:33.510
is better than watching

00:33:33.510 --> 00:33:34.500
irreversible damage

00:33:34.500 --> 00:33:35.200
happen,

00:33:35.230 --> 00:33:36.600
and then regretting it.

00:33:38.940 --> 00:33:41.190
Promoting the Mountain Patrol back then,

00:33:41.190 --> 00:33:43.920
writing articles to protect
Tibetan antelopes,

00:33:44.390 --> 00:33:45.690
and exposing Xinhai's illegal mining now—

00:33:45.690 --> 00:33:47.030
it's all the same to me.

00:33:47.550 --> 00:33:49.880
It's all for protecting the environment.

00:33:50.660 --> 00:33:52.720
It is something I must do

00:33:52.740 --> 00:33:53.870
at all costs.

00:33:55.090 --> 00:33:55.810
You say that when I do things,

00:33:55.810 --> 00:33:57.290
I don't think about Zhuling.

00:33:57.290 --> 00:33:59.220
Since she was born,

00:33:59.920 --> 00:34:01.020
everything I do,

00:34:01.050 --> 00:34:01.850
every single moment,

00:34:01.850 --> 00:34:02.980
I'm thinking of her.

00:34:03.510 --> 00:34:04.420
I'm doing this

00:34:04.510 --> 00:34:05.630
so when she grows up,

00:34:05.630 --> 00:34:06.430
I can tell her,

00:34:06.770 --> 00:34:07.660
regardless of ability

00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:08.540
or outcome,

00:34:09.030 --> 00:34:09.790
her father,

00:34:09.820 --> 00:34:10.980
when it was time to stand up,

00:34:10.980 --> 00:34:11.949
did not retreat.

00:34:12.210 --> 00:34:13.280
I did what an ordinary person

00:34:13.280 --> 00:34:14.420
should do.

00:34:22.110 --> 00:34:22.860
I know...

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:26.239
you've always wanted to be

00:34:26.239 --> 00:34:27.170
a good reporter.

00:34:28.900 --> 00:34:30.050
In Bolamula,

00:34:31.030 --> 00:34:32.960
that time we almost froze to death,

00:34:35.530 --> 00:34:36.360
I asked you,

00:34:37.840 --> 00:34:40.130
if you regretted entering the mountains.

00:34:40.130 --> 00:34:41.300
But you said

00:34:44.250 --> 00:34:44.820
you regretted

00:34:44.820 --> 00:34:47.080
not joining the Mountain Patrol sooner.

00:34:49.210 --> 00:34:50.340
Don't make fun of me.

00:34:52.150 --> 00:34:53.550
I'm not making fun of you.

00:34:59.920 --> 00:35:01.720
Bolamula is the highest place

00:35:03.150 --> 00:35:04.280
I have ever been.

00:35:06.750 --> 00:35:07.950
Not just in altitude.

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:10.420
Once you reach the peak,

00:35:10.420 --> 00:35:11.340
the only thing you can do

00:35:11.340 --> 00:35:12.340
is go down.

00:35:13.460 --> 00:35:14.210
Back then, I said

00:35:14.210 --> 00:35:16.670
I stayed in the provincial
capital for work.

00:35:16.750 --> 00:35:18.180
I separated from you and Zhuling.

00:35:18.180 --> 00:35:19.120
But in these past few years,

00:35:19.120 --> 00:35:20.380
I've achieved nothing

00:35:21.130 --> 00:35:22.460
and ended up here again.

00:35:23.610 --> 00:35:24.530
Like you said,

00:35:25.770 --> 00:35:27.370
if you don't finish the road,

00:35:28.040 --> 00:35:29.970
you can't reach your destination.

00:35:35.140 --> 00:35:36.500
I didn't say that.

00:35:40.540 --> 00:35:41.670
Captain did.

00:35:58.640 --> 00:36:01.060
[People's Hospital
Outpatient Building]

00:36:05.130 --> 00:36:06.260
There's no problem.

00:36:15.850 --> 00:36:16.560
Hua,

00:36:18.590 --> 00:36:19.900
don't take this money.

00:36:21.200 --> 00:36:22.060
Manager Bai...

00:36:23.020 --> 00:36:23.930
This isn't a simple

00:36:23.930 --> 00:36:24.930
safety accident.

00:36:27.210 --> 00:36:27.900
Xinhai

00:36:27.920 --> 00:36:29.120
did you wrong on this.

00:36:30.530 --> 00:36:32.260
It was definitely a violation.

00:36:32.270 --> 00:36:32.610
Whether

00:36:32.610 --> 00:36:34.050
you report it to the authorities

00:36:34.050 --> 00:36:35.380
or sue Xinhai,

00:36:36.220 --> 00:36:37.630
it is your right.

00:36:38.170 --> 00:36:39.560
I can help you find a lawyer.

00:36:39.560 --> 00:36:40.080
I believe you can—

00:36:40.080 --> 00:36:40.710
Manager Bai,

00:36:40.710 --> 00:36:41.460
thank you.

00:36:43.230 --> 00:36:43.790
But I...

00:36:52.450 --> 00:36:53.980
Besides the compensation,

00:36:55.160 --> 00:36:55.950
Mr. Meng also

00:36:55.970 --> 00:36:57.570
bought me a house in the city.

00:36:58.870 --> 00:36:59.540
He said

00:37:00.920 --> 00:37:03.250
my kid can transfer to
No. 2 Middle School.

00:37:03.790 --> 00:37:04.920
That's a good thing.

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:09.400
Even if I dug coal all my life,

00:37:10.610 --> 00:37:14.010
my kid wouldn't have been able to
get into No. 2 Middle School.

00:37:15.870 --> 00:37:16.930
Education is good.

00:37:18.340 --> 00:37:19.670
Go to a good high school,

00:37:21.570 --> 00:37:22.900
then a good university.

00:37:26.290 --> 00:37:27.500
I don't want my kid

00:37:28.780 --> 00:37:30.090
to live the way I have.

00:37:32.940 --> 00:37:33.870
Don't you agree?

00:37:48.420 --> 00:37:51.420
[Compensation Agreement]

00:37:51.980 --> 00:37:54.070
The money will be in your account soon.

00:37:54.070 --> 00:37:54.920
If you need help

00:37:54.920 --> 00:37:56.520
with anything in the future,

00:37:57.570 --> 00:37:58.570
just say the word.

00:38:01.320 --> 00:38:02.580
Take care of yourself.

00:38:12.840 --> 00:38:13.360
I'm off.

00:38:17.540 --> 00:38:18.350
Manager Bai,

00:38:21.600 --> 00:38:22.600
you're a good man.

00:38:28.260 --> 00:38:29.460
Generally speaking,

00:38:29.730 --> 00:38:31.090
the leadership of Tianduo

00:38:31.090 --> 00:38:32.190
attach great importance

00:38:32.190 --> 00:38:33.700
to environmental protection.

00:38:33.700 --> 00:38:34.920
The measures taken

00:38:35.270 --> 00:38:36.870
are powerful and effective.

00:38:37.960 --> 00:38:38.980
The ban on coal mining

00:38:38.980 --> 00:38:40.510
and ecological restoration work

00:38:40.510 --> 00:38:42.040
are progressing smoothly.

00:38:42.170 --> 00:38:43.170
Slope management

00:38:43.210 --> 00:38:44.610
and mine regreening work

00:38:44.630 --> 00:38:45.830
have had a good start.

00:38:46.780 --> 00:38:48.250
However, there are two matters

00:38:48.250 --> 00:38:50.390
I need to bring to everyone's attention.

00:38:50.390 --> 00:38:51.190
First,

00:38:51.960 --> 00:38:53.900
regarding Mingjia Chemical Factory's

00:38:53.900 --> 00:38:55.710
chemical gas leak incident,

00:38:55.820 --> 00:38:57.020
we issue a criticism.

00:38:57.570 --> 00:38:59.070
The municipal government must

00:38:59.070 --> 00:39:00.590
investigate liability as soon as possible

00:39:00.590 --> 00:39:02.800
handle it according to
laws and regulations,

00:39:02.800 --> 00:39:03.850
and submit a written report

00:39:03.850 --> 00:39:05.150
to the provincial government

00:39:05.150 --> 00:39:06.550
and include the results.

00:39:07.420 --> 00:39:08.340
Second,

00:39:08.460 --> 00:39:09.690
regarding the outcrop coal issue

00:39:09.690 --> 00:39:10.920
at Xinhai Coal Mine,

00:39:11.530 --> 00:39:12.980
the information we gathered

00:39:12.980 --> 00:39:14.440
through public surveys

00:39:15.050 --> 00:39:15.710
does not align with

00:39:15.710 --> 00:39:17.520
what the municipal government reported

00:39:17.520 --> 00:39:18.190
to us.

00:39:20.380 --> 00:39:20.980
Whether

00:39:21.000 --> 00:39:22.540
there are deeper issues,

00:39:23.070 --> 00:39:24.800
we cannot conclude at present.

00:39:25.650 --> 00:39:27.050
Although the inspection

00:39:27.130 --> 00:39:28.150
has ended,

00:39:28.980 --> 00:39:31.580
the inspection team will
continue to follow up

00:39:31.660 --> 00:39:33.660
and get to the bottom of this matter.

00:39:37.780 --> 00:39:39.000
We thank the inspection team

00:39:39.000 --> 00:39:40.300
for checking on our city's

00:39:40.300 --> 00:39:42.050
environmental protection work.

00:39:42.050 --> 00:39:42.760
Regarding the issues

00:39:42.760 --> 00:39:44.010
raised by the inspection team,

00:39:44.010 --> 00:39:45.090
we accept them all.

00:39:45.650 --> 00:39:48.110
We will promptly rectify them accordingly.

00:39:55.610 --> 00:39:56.320
Come in.

00:39:58.530 --> 00:40:00.220
Chief, you were looking for me?

00:40:00.220 --> 00:40:01.600
Good, very quick.

00:40:01.660 --> 00:40:02.000
Come on,

00:40:02.000 --> 00:40:03.200
let me introduce you.

00:40:03.760 --> 00:40:04.440
Sir,

00:40:04.910 --> 00:40:06.260
this is Bai Ju,

00:40:06.340 --> 00:40:07.510
whom I just mentioned.

00:40:07.510 --> 00:40:08.120
This is

00:40:08.150 --> 00:40:09.440
Mr. Huo, head of the
provincial environmental

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:10.230
inspection team.

00:40:10.230 --> 00:40:10.890
Hello, sir.

00:40:11.340 --> 00:40:11.880
Hello.

00:40:12.460 --> 00:40:12.760
This is—

00:40:12.760 --> 00:40:13.290
[Mu Zhonghe, Discipline Inspection
Commission of Qinghai Province]

00:40:13.290 --> 00:40:15.140
Mu Zhonghe of the Provincial
Discipline Inspection Commission.

00:40:15.140 --> 00:40:15.700
Hello, sir.

00:40:15.700 --> 00:40:16.190
Hello.

00:40:17.920 --> 00:40:18.360
Bai Ju,

00:40:18.880 --> 00:40:19.490
grab a chair.

00:40:19.490 --> 00:40:20.270
Let's sit and talk.

00:40:20.270 --> 00:40:20.670
Okay.

00:40:28.240 --> 00:40:28.970
Officer Bai,

00:40:29.820 --> 00:40:30.470
our

00:40:30.500 --> 00:40:31.940
environmental inspection of Tianduo City

00:40:31.940 --> 00:40:33.030
is coming to an end.

00:40:33.710 --> 00:40:34.970
There are some matters

00:40:34.980 --> 00:40:36.180
our colleague from the
Discipline Inspection Commission

00:40:36.180 --> 00:40:37.910
would like to discuss with you.

00:40:39.730 --> 00:40:40.480
Officer Bai,

00:40:41.230 --> 00:40:42.130
based on the complaint

00:40:42.130 --> 00:40:42.980
we received

00:40:43.340 --> 00:40:44.110
and this

00:40:44.210 --> 00:40:45.670
inspection in Tianduo,

00:40:46.010 --> 00:40:46.970
we suspect that

00:40:47.360 --> 00:40:48.800
there are major issues

00:40:49.280 --> 00:40:50.680
behind Xinhai Coal Mine.

00:40:51.670 --> 00:40:52.570
Since we currently

00:40:52.570 --> 00:40:54.090
lack solid evidence,

00:40:54.510 --> 00:40:55.320
we have requested

00:40:55.320 --> 00:40:56.650
support and assistance

00:40:56.690 --> 00:40:58.380
from the Municipal Public Security Bureau

00:40:58.380 --> 00:40:58.800
to secretly

00:40:58.800 --> 00:41:00.460
investigate Xinhai's issues

00:41:00.590 --> 00:41:01.690
after we leave

00:41:01.950 --> 00:41:03.320
Tianduo City.

00:41:06.130 --> 00:41:07.440
We have reported this matter

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:08.390
to the provincial leadership

00:41:08.390 --> 00:41:09.250
in charge

00:41:09.400 --> 00:41:10.210
and the Provincial

00:41:10.210 --> 00:41:11.360
Public Security Department.

00:41:11.360 --> 00:41:12.530
They all agreed.

00:41:14.310 --> 00:41:15.680
You are more familiar with the situation

00:41:15.680 --> 00:41:16.390
at Xinhai.

00:41:16.890 --> 00:41:17.720
You are the best fit

00:41:17.720 --> 00:41:18.720
for this mission.

00:41:19.180 --> 00:41:20.190
This investigation

00:41:20.190 --> 00:41:21.590
isn't just about Xinhai,

00:41:22.220 --> 00:41:24.020
but also the umbrella behind it.

00:41:24.230 --> 00:41:25.820
The provincial leadership
has instructed that

00:41:25.820 --> 00:41:26.800
there shall be

00:41:26.920 --> 00:41:28.430
no exceptions to Party discipline

00:41:28.430 --> 00:41:29.290
and state laws.

00:41:29.570 --> 00:41:30.540
No matter who is involved,

00:41:30.540 --> 00:41:32.140
whatever their background,

00:41:32.140 --> 00:41:33.550
we must get to the bottom of it.

00:41:33.550 --> 00:41:34.280
Understood.

00:41:34.850 --> 00:41:36.250
I appreciate your trust.

00:41:36.610 --> 00:41:38.340
I promise to complete the task.

00:41:39.580 --> 00:41:41.180
We must not alert them before

00:41:41.410 --> 00:41:42.900
having obtained evidence.

00:41:42.900 --> 00:41:43.870
The smaller the target

00:41:43.870 --> 00:41:44.800
and the fewer the people,

00:41:44.800 --> 00:41:46.730
the better for the investigation.

00:41:46.730 --> 00:41:47.330
Of course,

00:41:47.780 --> 00:41:48.980
given that the situation at Xinhai

00:41:48.980 --> 00:41:49.980
is quite complex,

00:41:50.910 --> 00:41:52.370
you can have a few

00:41:52.480 --> 00:41:53.210
assistants.

00:41:53.610 --> 00:41:54.420
Also,

00:41:54.490 --> 00:41:55.610
for your safety,

00:41:55.780 --> 00:41:56.460
you may carry

00:41:56.460 --> 00:41:57.430
a pistol, handcuffs,

00:41:57.430 --> 00:41:58.500
and other police equipment

00:41:58.500 --> 00:42:00.560
while executing the investigation.

00:42:02.510 --> 00:42:03.070
Chief,

00:42:04.150 --> 00:42:05.840
I'd like to request for a comrade

00:42:05.840 --> 00:42:07.220
from outside the police system

00:42:07.220 --> 00:42:08.280
to be my assistant.

00:42:09.610 --> 00:42:10.740
Your Mountain Patrol teammates

00:42:10.740 --> 00:42:11.490
won't do.

00:42:12.850 --> 00:42:14.910
I'd like to recommend my ex-husband,

00:42:15.150 --> 00:42:15.920
Shao Yunfei,

00:42:16.010 --> 00:42:16.860
a reporter for Western Evening News

00:42:16.860 --> 00:42:17.860
based in Tianduo.

00:42:19.050 --> 00:42:20.580
He is politically reliable

00:42:20.690 --> 00:42:21.400
and highly sensitive

00:42:21.400 --> 00:42:22.860
to environmental issues.

00:42:23.110 --> 00:42:24.170
More importantly,

00:42:24.590 --> 00:42:25.320
he has done many reports

00:42:25.320 --> 00:42:26.470
on Xinhai.

00:42:26.810 --> 00:42:27.500
Also,

00:42:27.760 --> 00:42:29.080
his identity as a reporter

00:42:29.080 --> 00:42:30.880
also provides excellent cover.

00:42:32.880 --> 00:42:33.490
Chief Shi,

00:42:33.900 --> 00:42:34.690
I think

00:42:35.130 --> 00:42:35.820
Officer Bai's request

00:42:35.820 --> 00:42:36.680
is reasonable.

00:42:39.070 --> 00:42:39.930
It's approved.

00:42:42.340 --> 00:42:42.940
Chief,

00:42:43.550 --> 00:42:44.920
I believe there is one person

00:42:44.920 --> 00:42:46.010
who should be a major suspect

00:42:46.010 --> 00:42:47.570
in this case we are investigating.

00:42:47.570 --> 00:42:48.170
This person

00:42:48.170 --> 00:42:50.320
is also linked to Xinhai's illegal mining.

00:42:50.320 --> 00:42:50.820
I request permission

00:42:50.820 --> 00:42:52.550
to put him under surveillance.

00:42:53.880 --> 00:42:55.680
You can buy anything over there.

00:42:56.340 --> 00:42:57.300
Why go through all this trouble

00:42:57.300 --> 00:42:58.160
to mail it over?

00:42:58.190 --> 00:42:59.270
What if they don't like it?

00:42:59.270 --> 00:43:00.020
Why bother?

00:43:00.200 --> 00:43:00.950
It shows

00:43:00.980 --> 00:43:01.980
that we care.

00:43:02.940 --> 00:43:05.100
You can't get this hardcover edition

00:43:05.200 --> 00:43:07.600
of the Four Great Classical Novels abroad.

00:43:07.860 --> 00:43:08.880
I'm going out for a bit.